00049     struct {
00050         xed_uint32_t cf:1;

00064         
00065         xed_uint32_t iopl:2;

00067         xed_uint32_t must_be_0c:1;
00068

00073

00077         
00078         xed_uint32_t must_be_0e:4;  
00079 
00080         // fc0,fc1,fc2,fc3 are not really part of rflags but I put them

00082         // instructions.
00083         xed_uint32_t fc0:1;  
00084         xed_uint32_t fc1:1;  
00085         xed_uint32_t fc2:1;  
00086         xed_uint32_t fc3:1;  
00087     } s;

00089 };
